data.description: Check out this amazing new listing including large backyard in Chattahoochee school district. Main level features 2 story foyer with open concept, family room & fireplace with built-in bookcases. The space is flexible offering formal living room, formal dining-room, both with wainscoting, private office with french doors, tray ceilings, half bath powder room, with hard surface floors throughout. Kitchen offers updated granite counter-tops, ss/black appliances, pantry, and eat-in breakfast room. Owner's suite boasts soaring ceilings, large bathroom with double oversized vanity, tile, garden soaking tub and double stand-up shower, private toilet room, and spacious walk-in closet. Secondary bedrooms are generous in size with full guest bathroom to share.  Windgate is a swim/tennis neighborhood convenient to Avalon, Halcyon, GA 400,Emory Hospital, Lake Lanier, and North Georgia Mountains.
